article_title: Six-year-old Gazan girl found dead days after plea for help
sentence: A  six-year-old  girl  who  went  missing  in  Gaza  City  last  month  has  been  found  dead,  along  with  several  of  her  relatives  and  two  paramedics  who  tried  to  save  her,  after  they  appear  to  have  come  under  fire  from  Israeli  tanks.

sentence: Its  crew  -  Yusuf  al-Zeino  and  Ahmed  al-Madhoun  -  were  killed  when  the  ambulance  was  bombed  by  Israeli  forces,  the  organisation  says.
